This repository is for the PeoplePulseBotDemo 
(an assistant to converse with employees over messaging apps to get satisfaction data)

Instructions for Use:
To install dependencies, in the root directory run:

	npm install core-js
	npm install restify
	npm install botbuilder
	npm install fs


To run the application call:

	node app.js

To interact with the bot download the Bot Framework Emulator at: 

	https://github.com/Microsoft/BotFramework-Emulator/releases/tag/v3.5.35

	Download the botframework-emulator-Setup-3.5.35.exe file. 
	